{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n800\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 0 + 0 = 648\u2081\u2080\n\n335\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 243 + 27 + 5 = 275\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n648 \u00d7 275 = 648 \u00d7 (300 - 25)\n= 648 \u00d7 300 - 648 \u00d7 25\n= 194,400 - 16,200\n= 178,200\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n178200 \u00f7 9 = 19800 r 0\n19800 \u00f7 9 = 2200 r 0\n2200 \u00f7 9 = 244 r 4\n244 \u00f7 9 = 27 r 1\n27 \u00f7 9 = 3 r 0\n3 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 3\n\nReading from bottom to top: 301400\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n301400\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u2075 + 0\u00d79\u2074 + 1\u00d79\u00b3 + 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070\n= 3\u00d759049 + 0 + 1\u00d7729 + 4\u00d781 + 0 + 0\n= 177147 + 729 + 324\n= 178200\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n301400", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 480}